---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			:root {
				/* Brighter, clearer blue for the permanent highlight */
				--highlight-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); 
				--highlight-text: #1e40af;
			}
			main {
				width: calc(100% - 2em);
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: auto;
				padding: 4em 1em;
				line-height: 1.7;
				color: #334155;
				animation: slideUp 0.6s ease-out;
			}
			h1 {
				font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
				font-weight: 900;
				letter-spacing: -0.02em;
				margin-bottom: 0.75em;
				color: #0f172a;
				background: linear-gradient(to right, #1d4ed8, #3b82f6);
				-webkit-background-clip: text;
				-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
			}
			p {
				margin-bottom: 1.5em;
				font-size: 1.2rem;
			}
			ul {
				background: #f8fafc;
				padding: 2.5em;
				border-radius: 16px;
				border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
				list-style-type: '✨';
			}
			li {
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				padding-left: 0.5rem;
			}
			code {
				background: #f1f5f9;
				padding: 0.2em 0.5em;
				border-radius: 6px;
				font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
				font-size: 0.95em;
				border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
			}

			/* --- The Fixed Full Blue Highlight Style --- */
			a {
				text-decoration: none;      /* Removes the actual underline mark */
				color: var(--highlight-text);
				font-weight: 700;
				padding: 2px 4px;           /* Adds space around text for the highlight */
				margin: 0 -2px;             /* Offsets padding to keep text alignment */
				border-radius: 4px;         /* Smooth edges for the highlight */
				
				/* Full Background Highlight */
				background-color: var(--highlight-color);
				
				transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
			}

			a:hover {
				background-color: #3b82f6; /* Solid blue on hover */
				color: #ffffff;            /* White text on hover */
				box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
			}

			@keyframes slideUp {
				from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
				to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Hello, Astronaut!</h1>
			<p>
				Welcome to the official <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a> blog starter template. This
				template serves as a lightweight, minimally-styled starting point for anyone looking to build
				a personal website, blog, or portfolio with Astro.
			</p>
			<p>
				This template comes with a few integrations already configured in your
				<code>astro.config.mjs</code> file. You can customize your setup with
				<a href="https://astro.build/integrations">Astro Integrations</a> to add tools like Tailwind,
				React, or Vue to your project.
			</p>
			<p>Here are a few ideas on how to get started with the template:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Edit this page in <code>src/pages/index.astro</code></li>
				<li>Edit the site header items in <code>src/components/Header.astro</code></li>
				<li>Add your name to the footer in <code>src/components/Footer.astro</code></li>
				<li>Check out the included blog posts in <code>src/content/blog/</code></li>
				<li>Customize the blog post page layout in <code>src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code></li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				If you want websites like that contact us at <a href="https://aevasoft.com"
					>AevaSoft Technologies
				</a> or <a href="mailto:info@aevasoft.com">email us</a> to ask questions.
			</p>
			<p>
				Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out <a
					href="https://github.com/Danyal-Raza/astro-blog-starter-template"
					>astro-blog-template-repo
				</a> by <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/syed-danyal-raza-b80271264">Syed Danyal Raza</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
